Description: dock-style launcher and task manager for Plasma 6
 Lattecotta Dock is a Plasma 6 and Qt 6 continuation of Latte Dock. It
 provides multiple layouts, task management, launchers, indicator themes,
 and parabolic icon effects on the Plasma Wayland desktop.
